# Book Nest – Online Book Store UI

A simple bookstore-themed website layout with featured books and interactive styling.

## 📌 Features

- Navigation bar with search field
- Banner image section
- Featured books grid
- Hover effects on cards
- Button styling
- Responsive flex layout

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Flexbox
- Basic hover animations

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a web browser.
2. Hover over book cards to see interactive effects.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Layout structuring
- Card design
- Hover transitions
- UI alignment
- Basic e-commerce style interface

